snippet.title: rIVerse Reacts: How You Like That + Sour Candy by BLACKPINK (DOUBLE FEATURE)
snippet.description:
WELCOME BACK TO #rIVerseReacts 🤩

We are back on the muthaf**king couch b*tchhh and we literally couldn't be happier to be in each others’ physical presence again 😢! Not to mention, we have returned with the legendary #BLACKPINK and it’s a Double Feature y’all!! POW💥 'How You Like That' & 'Sour Candy' (Lady Gaga featuring the girls). We don't know if we’ll still have our wigs by the end of this reaction 😱!! 

Did we #PlaylistORNah?!?

Let us know in the comments below what your favourite moments are from this reaction.

http://www.youtube.com/riverselive
